    "epitet": "Masked Rider",
    "description": "Cherche's son. Unaccustomed to interpersonal interactions. His wyvern Minerva belonged to his late mother. Appears in Fire Emblem Awakening.",
    "artist": "Meka (めか)",
    "voiceActorEN": "Orion Acaba",
    "voiceActorJP": "新垣樽助",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I'm Gerome, Cherche's son. You should know I have no intention of getting involved with this world.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "My parents are no longer with me. My mother went off to battle, but only her wyvern Minerva returned... And she had suffered many wounds.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I only came here so I could release Minerva—not to get caught up in the affairs of some other world. So why is it I must help you?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "You work too hard. Why is that? You're from another world as well, are you not?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "As a Summoner, maybe you can call upon my deceased parents... No, forget I said anything. It's foolish...",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "The ends of my cloak were beginning to fray, so I was mending the fabric. ...You look surprised to learn I can sew.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "You are <Player Name>? Greetings from <Friend Name>. Is sending people back and forth like this fun for you?",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "You seem pleased as well, Minerva.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "It's a start.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "...Hmph. Fate is feeling stingy today.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "This is much too valuable. Maybe someone else should have it.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "You've come to chat yet again? Some people just can't take a hint. And now it seems Minerva has taken a liking to you, against my wishes. Yet, I suppose I cannot be cruel to someone Minerva approves of. As I've said before, I have no desire to meddle in the affairs of other worlds. If Askr is destined to fall... then so be it. However, if you truly wish to protect this world and its inhabitants, then Minerva and I will be by your side. After all... We understand the pain of loss all too well.",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
